aces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bcc3ffb7378b4325ad7f384481f13a077072565","tid":320800,"uid":118322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T09:30:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5b9f9fd132b6cfc875c5e40cc3a1dfa9fcbd0068","tid":320800,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T09:32:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Cccu見</blockquote><br />\n姐係HD仲好過樹仁大學？</blockquote><br />\n諗清楚係咪有心讀/做，search下都已經好多資料，你依家先問？</blockquote><br />\n我fd係真心真心想讀社工既，不過見有d人話樹仁好，有d人話唔好，想問清楚姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樹仁好"},{"pid":"c51fa82574bfbd82f297231c185fef572792c153","tid":320800,"uid":114146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T09:39:23.000Z","msg":"大學同hd比你揀，仲洗揀嘅？"},{"pid":"85544c9246a575f367b9a44dcb4eded3d638f6a5","tid":320800,"uid":77630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:45:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大學同hd比你揀，仲洗揀嘅？</blockquote><br />\nhd社工比較好<br />\n因為好多老師有心教  同學亦有心有力參與社會運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n眼見好多大學社工淨係識得玩，老師又教得差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4d481823584d70a3dcf240e449b21d66d7e6c2","tid":320800,"uid":46047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T12:56:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>代朋友問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樹仁社工定其他院校HD社會比較好？<br />\n朋友利申：combine cert 21分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇你點樣定義好同壞，每間學校既社工有佢地既特式<br />\n<br />\n留意係HKCC社工HD唔收人住<br />\nIVE社工暫時睇到FULL左<br />\n其他院校(E.G. 明愛 / 港專 / CCCU)可以考慮"}]}